<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141979' id='t-141979'>on the edge of a crater, Gunung Batur.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='145806' id='t-145806'>And I was in a village where there was</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148823' id='t-148823'>an initiation ceremony for the young men,</span>
