<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='155731' id='t-155731'>And as I sat in this temple square</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='158190' id='t-158190'>under this gigantic beringin banyan tree,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='161190' id='t-161190'>in the dark, there was no
