<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='172064' id='t-172064'>as I listened to the gamelan music</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='174107' id='t-174107'>from all the different villagers that came</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176156' id='t-176156'>for this once-every-five-years ceremony.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='179554' id='t-179554'>And I thought I was alone
