<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='183149' id='t-183149'>And all of a sudden, out of the dark,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='185980' id='t-185980'>from the other end of the square,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187864' id='t-187864'>I saw the glint of mirrors
lit by the moon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='191772' id='t-191772'>And these 20 old men who I'd seen before</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195331' id='t-195331'>all of a sudden stood up in these
