<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207480' id='t-207480'>No one was there, and they came out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='209841' id='t-209841'>and they did this incredible dance.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='213480' id='t-213480'>&quot;Huhuhuhuhuhuhuhahahahaha.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='217172' id='t-217172'>And they moved their bodies
