<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226563' id='t-226563'>and performing, creating, and I went,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='229777' id='t-229777'>&quot;Who are they performing for</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231920' id='t-231920'>with these elaborate costumes,</span>
