<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247380' id='t-247380'>There was no money involved.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='249631' id='t-249631'>It wasn't going to be written down.
It was no news.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='252851' id='t-252851'>And there were these incredible artists</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='254997' id='t-254997'>that felt for me like an eternity
