<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='272861' id='t-272861'>And they put on an opera all night long.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='275399' id='t-275399'>Human beings needed the light.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='277659' id='t-277659'>They needed the light to see.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280296' id='t-280296'>So what I gained and gathered
