<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='286556' id='t-286556'>was that you must be true</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289879' id='t-289879'>to what you believe as an artist
all the way through,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293951' id='t-293951'>but you also have to be aware</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='297490' id='t-297490'>that the audience is out there
in our lives at this time,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='300979' id='t-300979'>and they also need the light.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302384' id='t-302384'>And it's this incredible balance</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='304547' id='t-304547'>that I think that we walk</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306296' id='t-306296'>when we are creating something
