<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='320112' id='t-320112'>that I have walked my whole life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322742' id='t-322742'>What I would like to do now is to tell you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325290' id='t-325290'>a little bit</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327096' id='t-327096'>about how I work.
