<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='329953' id='t-329953'>You saw many examples of my work up there,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='332205' id='t-332205'>but it's one that people know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='334150' id='t-334150'>I start with the notion of the ideograph.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='336849' id='t-336849'>An ideograph is like a brush
